The main features of SMW+ can be classified as follows:

* '''[[Help:Knowledge_Authoring|Knowledge Authoring]].''' Features that enable users to easily add semantic data to the wiki.
* '''[[Help:Knowledge_Retrieval|Knowledge Retrieval]].''' Features to query knowledge stored in the wiki.
* '''[[Help:Maintenance|Maintenance]].''' Tools to keep the wiki clean and consistent.
* '''[[Help:Administration|Administration]].''' Features that support general administrative tasks.
* '''[[Help:Usability|Usability]].''' General user-friendly features that improve the wiki's operability.
* '''[[Help:Ontology_Management|Ontology Management]].''' Import and export of OWL ontologies.
* '''[[Help:Search|Search]].''' Integration of various search technologies for better information retrieval.